# rudderstack_retl_source_s3_table (Resource)

A RETL (Reverse ETL) source backed by an S3 bucket. RudderStack reads objects under the (optional) `object_prefix` from the configured bucket and syncs the resulting records to the connected destinations.

`primary_key` is optional for S3 sources. If supplied, it is used to track row-level changes between syncs.

